---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`页面未找到 | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="请求的页面不存在或已移动。" noindex />
    <style>
      .not-found {
        max-width: 42rem;
        margin: 3.5rem auto 4rem;
        padding: 0 1rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .not-found .code {
        margin: 0;
        color: #d63d2e;
        font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 5rem);
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        line-height: 1;
      }
      .not-found h1 {
        margin: 0.8rem 0 0.6rem;
        font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
      }
      .not-found p {
        margin: 0 auto 1.4rem;
        max-width: 30rem;
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
        line-height: 1.65;
      }
      .not-found-actions {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.7rem;
      }
      .not-found-actions a {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 2.6rem;
        padding: 0.55rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: #fff;
        color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
        font-weight: 800;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .not-found-actions a.primary {
        border-color: rgba(214, 61, 46, 0.35);
        background: #fff7f5;
        color: #d63d2e;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main class="not-found">
      <p class="code">404</p>
      <h1>页面未找到</h1>
      <p>这个地址没有对应文章或栏目。可能是链接写错、大小写不匹配，或内容已下线。请从首页或研究列表重新进入。</p>
      <div class="not-found-actions">
        <a class="primary" href="/">返回首页</a>
        <a href="/stock-analysis/">A股分析</a>
        <a href="/us-stock-analysis/">美股分析</a>
        <a href="/serenity/">白发股神</a>
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
